Package com.project.CyShare.app

Class Maps

java.lang.Object
com.project.CyShare.app.Maps
@Entity public class Maps extends Object
Map entity class that is used to hold location coordinates in the form of latitude and longitude. It's linked to a User entity.
Author:
Bhuwan Joshi
